OL,6,FThis story contains an image of a stab
OL,7,Fwound which readers might find
OL,8,Fdistressing.
OL,10,FA young soldier who had to give up his
OL,11,Fdream job in the army after being
OL,12,Fstabbed says he "still thinks about
OL,13,Fthe attack every day".
OL,15,FChris Griffith from Llandrygarn,
OL,16,FAnglesey almost died after he was
OL,17,Fstabbed with a knife on 7 January
OL,18,F2022, in Tan-yr-Efail, Holyhead.
