OL,3,CTeenage soldier gave up dream job in
OL,4,Cthe army after being stabbed
OL,6,FSpeaking to S4C's current affairs
OL,7,Fprogramme, Y Byd ar Bedwar, Chris said
OL,8,Fthat the stabbing has "changed
OL,9,Feverything". Chris was 17 at the time
OL,10,Fof the incident.
OL,12,F'He got me'
OL,14,FChris went to Tan-yr-Efail that night
OL,15,Fto meet a boy he knew from his time at
OL,16,Fschool, to discuss a disagreement over
OL,17,Fa girl.
OL,19,F"He asked me to shake his hand, so I
OL,20,Fdid - and that's when he got me and
OL,21,Fran away."
