OL,3,CTeenage soldier gave up dream job in
OL,4,Cthe army after being stabbed
OL,6,FChris was stabbed in his stomach
OL,7,Fbetween his prostate gland and the
OL,8,Fintestine, with a knife that measured
OL,9,F8 centimetres.
OL,11,FHe was rushed to Ysbyty Gwynedd by his
OL,12,Ffriend where he was treated for
OL,13,Fserious injuries.
OL,15,FWhile in hospital, Chris underwent a
OL,16,Ffour-hour operation, during which he
OL,17,Flost a quarter of his blood.
OL,19,F'I thought I was dying'
