OL,3,CTeenage soldier gave up dream job in
OL,4,Cthe army after being stabbed
OL,6,F"That was my life, and now it's a
OL,7,Fdifferent life."
OL,9,F"I think about it every night, I
OL,10,Fhaven't gone a day without thinking
OL,11,Fabout what happened... It takes all my
OL,12,Fmotivation.
OL,14,F"For two years my life was just army
OL,15,Farmy army, but leaving the army and
OL,16,Ftrying to find a new job was a
OL,17,Fchallenge," Chris added.
