OL,6,FA freedom of information request by Y
OL,7,FByd ar Bedwar revealed:
OL,9,FGerallt Wyn Jones, who teaches self-
OL,10,Fdefence workshops for children and
OL,11,Fyoung people in North Wales is worried
OL,12,Fabout the situation.
OL,14,F"The reason I have done a session with
OL,15,Fknives is because it seems that it is
OL,16,Fon the rise from what we see in the
OL,17,Fmedia. I am worried about what is
OL,18,Fhappening in the area."
