OL,3,CTeenage soldier gave up dream job in
OL,4,Cthe army after being stabbed
OL,6,F"Nobody wins in a fight involving a
OL,7,Fknife. Someone gets into a lot of
OL,8,Ftrouble and the other is going to get
OL,9,Fhurt or die - so there are no winners."
OL,11,FJames Rees was sent to a Young
OL,12,FOffenders Institution after being
OL,13,Fsentenced to nine years for grievous
OL,14,Fbodily harm after stabbing Chris, and
OL,15,F18 months for having a dangerous
OL,16,Fweapon in a public place.
OL,18,FHe has also received an order not to
OL,19,Fcontact Chris ever again.
